        "      \"Projection : WGS84 (EPSG:4326)  |  Sources : Natural Earth, GADM v4.1\\n\",\n",
        "      \"Hydrographie : HydroSHEDS / approximation. Routes : OpenStreetMap.\"\n",
        "    )\n",
